00:06:02.839 --> 00:06:04.839
So my factors are going to stay as factors.

00:06:04.839 --> 00:06:05.839
My dates are going to stay as dates.

00:06:05.839 --> 00:06:07.839
My date times are going to stay as date times.

00:06:07.839 --> 00:06:09.839
So really recommend doing this.

00:06:09.839 --> 00:06:13.839
